 Multiplication of complex numbers is commutative.  Axiom for real and complex numbers, derived from set theory.  This construction-dependent theorem should not be referenced directly, nor should the proven axiom ~ ax-mulcom be used later.  Instead, use ~ mulcom .  (Contributed by NM, 31-Aug-1995.)  (New usage is discouraged.)
